WEBVTT

00:01:58.566 --> 00:02:00.946
He kept getting all the things he desired.

00:02:00.946 --> 00:02:03.600
For about two months
he was very happy,

00:02:03.600 --> 00:02:05.690
but then gradually
his happiness started dwindling.

00:02:05.690 --> 00:02:10.796
But because things happened
just the way he wanted,

00:02:12.040 --> 00:02:18.376
the play of ups and downs in life
was over and so was the fun.

00:02:18.400 --> 00:02:23.616
Finally one day he called
his faithful servant and said,

00:02:23.640 --> 00:02:27.496
“Honestly, I am bored
of living in this heaven.”

00:02:27.520 --> 00:02:32.400
He had decided since all his wishes
came true this must be heaven.